    <briefdescription>
<para>Constraint for integer-valued knobs. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Validates that integer knob values are within a specified range and/or match allowed values. Supports min/max bounds, step increments, and explicit allowed value lists. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
